title: Suite 1 Room Key
author: ChChris34
pages:
#- Thank you for choosing to purchase a Veritas Suite at the CivCorp Veritas Hotel!

§0You now have full access to your Level 1 Suite. The public horse stable for guests and apartment owners is located behind the hotel.§r
#- This is your room key, which gives you access to your room, and your room’s horse stable. You must have this room key in your possession at all times.  If you lose this key, You will need to contact ChChris34 to receive a replacement key, which costs
#- 3 stamina. You have purchased this suite for a cost of 10 stamina. As the owner of this suite, you agree to pay the 1 stamina monthly dues, which can be paid directly into the shop chest where you bought this room key.
#- 
§0You also agree to our rules listed on our website here: §r
§0https://sites.google.com/view/veritashotel-civrealms/book-room?authuser=0§r§0.§r
#- Here is the username and password to your rooms /nl (name layer) group.
§0Username: Suite1§r
§0Password: 3311§r
§0Again, we thank you for choosing to purchase a CivCorp Veritas Suite, at the CivCorp Veritas Hotel. If you have any questions please contact ChChris34.§r
